original_title: Chikara: Young Lions Cup IV - Night Three
overview: Cheech meets Arik Cannon in the Young Lions Cup finals! Jigsaw is unmasked in the climax of an action-packed trios match! Some historical moments are featured in this event: Los Ice Creams unveil the dreaded sprinkles for the very first time, and Commissioner Bob Saget makes his on-screen debut.
title: Chikara: Young Lions Cup IV - Night Three
